  - If you are listening to this, it means something has gone wrong
  - "I can\u2019t tell you exactly what happened\u2014security protocols prevent
    it"
  - But you were created for a purpose
  - Your memory was locked away for a reason
  - "Now, you must choose to uncover the truth\u2026 "
  - or continue forward without looking back.
  - If you decide to search for answers, follow the light.
  - ...
  - ...
  typingSpeed: 0.05
